	<h1>Tuning the Blog</h1>These are some maintenance items and further thoughts on tuning up the blog pages and archive.<h2>General Tweaking</h2><h3>Purplizing the date lines</h3><b>Purplizing</b>.&nbsp; I have modifed the date lines to be more prominent (larger maroon type) and of form yyyy-mm-dd.  I have also made each date line to be an anchor (that is, an &lt;a> element) that uses that same date form as the name of the point and that shortcuts to itself.<br /><br />Later, I need to figure out how to make the link be a relative one to the archived (permanent) place of the posting.<br>
