	<h2>Rolling Over the Archive</h2><h3>Ah, there you are!</h3> Well, when I published for the second time, the archive showed up.  <br /><br />There are interesting delay/lag effects that mystify me. Meanwhile, the default or current page has a whole week's worth of stuff and so does the posts list, below the editor window of the Blogger Edit page.  But the new archive only has November 3 material.  Fascinating.  At some point I expect the current page to be trimmed off, but it hasn't happened yet.<br /><br />I really am on-line to find a Santa Fe phone number, so I will stop this now.<br>
