	<h3>So where is it?</h3> Ah, more inscrutibility.  I love it. Yes it is a new week, my timestamp archive links are to a new archive page, and it isn't there.  Hmm. Hmm.  Also, viewing my posts here in the Blogger editor shows continuity back through all of the dates.  When I view the current page it takes me all the way back to the very beginning and my first post too.  So, there is something I don't get about archive roll-over, just yet. <br /><br />The odd part is that the November 3 posts are linked to a November 3 archive page, and it isn't there.<br>
